OL,3,CNew laws to crack down on disruptive
OL,4,Cprotests come into force
OL,6,FNew public order powers to prevent
OL,7,F"disruptive" protests will come into
OL,8,Fforce from Friday.
OL,10,FThe Serious Disruption Prevention
OL,11,FOrders will aim to prevent individuals
OL,12,Ffrom repeatedly causing serious
OL,13,Fdisruption at protests.
OL,15,FCivil liberties organisation Liberty
OL,16,Fdescribed the legislation as "a
OL,17,Fshameless attempt" by the Government
OL,18,Fto reduce the right to protest.
