OL,3,CNew laws to crack down on disruptive
OL,4,Cprotests come into force
OL,6,F"However, recent months have shown
OL,7,Fcertain individuals are just dedicated
OL,8,Fto wreaking havoc and causing severe
OL,9,Fdisruption to the everyday lives of
OL,10,Fthe public.
OL,12,F"This is why we have introduced these
OL,13,Fnew powers to ensure that anyone who
OL,14,Fignores warnings from our law
OL,15,Fenforcement cannot continue to cause
OL,16,Fturmoil unpunished."
OL,18,FThe introduction of the new orders is
OL,19,Fthe latest step in the government's
OL,20,Fcrackdown on "disruptive protests".
