OL,3,CNew laws to crack down on disruptive
OL,4,Cprotests come into force
OL,6,FJodie Beck, policy and campaigns
OL,7,Fofficer at Liberty, said: "These
OL,8,Fmeasures are a shameless attempt to
OL,9,Fprevent people from being able to make
OL,10,Ftheir voices heard on the issues that
OL,11,Fmatter most to them.
OL,13,F"In recent years, the Government has
OL,14,Frepeatedly introduced new laws which
OL,15,Fhave reduced our right to protest.
