OL,3,CNew laws to crack down on disruptive
OL,4,Cprotests come into force
OL,6,FUnder public order legislation,
OL,7,Fserious disruption may occur when
OL,8,Fprotest activity prevents or hinders
OL,9,Fday-to-day activities, construction or
OL,10,Fmaintenance works, causes delays to
OL,11,Fdeliveries of time-sensitive products
OL,12,For disrupts access to essential goods
OL,13,Fand services in a way that is more
OL,14,Fthan minor.
